# NYI: TODO: comment
#
# HTTP/1.1 as defined in
# * HTTP/1.1        https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc9112
# * HTTP Semantics  https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc9110
# * HTTP Caching    https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc9111
